Text: Thanks for all the uploads Fishcat, you're awesome!

Once again fishcat, just wanted to say thank you for all your efforts this season.  The show isn't broadcast in the UK at all so if it hadn't been for you, I wouldn't have been able to appreciate the star that Sharon Needles is ! :)

Thank you for being the only reliable up-loader for RPDR. I don't have the proper station in Canada so this is the only way I can watch. Much appreciated - hope to see more of you when 'All-Stars' and 'Season 5' start later.

As an aside, would it be possible to upload Drag U? Seasons 1 and 2?
